            <li>Filtering </li>
            <li>Column (resizing, reorder, show/hide columns) </li>
            <li>Searching </li>
            <li>TreeColumnIndex </li>
        </ul>
    </p>
    <p>More information on the state management can be found in this <a aria-label="Navigate to the documentation for state management in the tree grid component" target='_blank' href='https://blazor.syncfusion.com/documentation/treegrid/state-management/'>documentation</a> section.</p>
</ActionDescription>

